{"stat": "ok", "comments": {"comment": [{"permalink": "http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/2162923785/#comment72157622721819034", "realname": "", "path_alias": null, "author": "25695066@N00", "iconserver": "7037", "datecreate": "1257214087", "_content": "The name of the pilot is Robert Grant &quot;Bob&quot; Fowler, not &quot;Bowler&quot;, and he is sitting in a Wright Model B Flyer he named the &quot;Cole Flyer&quot;.", "authorname": "TVL1970", "id": "8602872-2162923785-72157622721819034", "iconfarm": 8}, {"permalink": "http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/2162923785/#comment72157622725776878", "realname": "", "path_alias": "ryan_loc", "author": "35234565@N04", "iconserver": "1021", "datecreate": "1257266191", "_content": "TVL 1970: Absolutely.  Thanks for pointing this out.  We'll make the correction to the name the next time we update the record.", "authorname": "Ryan (LOC P&P)", "id": "8602872-2162923785-72157622725776878", "iconfarm": 2}, {"permalink": "http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/2162923785/#comment72157631121706418", "realname": "Art Siegel", "path_alias": "artolog", "author": "76016463@N00", "iconserver": "3807", "datecreate": "1345268015", "_content": "see notes under <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/2163728542/\" title=\"Lathrop, Burns, Nixon, Henderson, French, Grundy, B. Fowler, J.J. Cole, W.L. Colt, Henderson, and Stratton [around plane] (LOC) by The Library of Congress, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm3.staticflickr.com/2412/2163728542_8dcff37230_m.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"173\" alt=\"Lathrop, Burns, Nixon, Henderson, French, Grundy, B. Fowler, J.J. Cole, W.L. Colt, Henderson, and Stratton [around plane] (LOC)\" /></a>\n\nThis is J.J. Cole's &quot;Cole Flyer&quot;, which was a Wright biplane with one of Cole's auto engines driving it.  Cole hired Fowler to pilot it in a transcontinental race in September, 1911, the date on the photo.\n\nAnother from the same day:\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/2162904877/\" title=\"J.J. Cole; Bob Fowler; &amp; W.F. Grundy [plane] (LOC) by The Library of Congress, on Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm3.staticflickr.com/2234/2162904877_799fab2b14_m.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"178\" alt=\"J.J. Cole; Bob Fowler; &amp; W.F. Grundy [plane] (LOC)\" /></a>", "authorname": "artolog", "id": "8602872-2162923785-72157631121706418", "iconfarm": 4}, {"permalink": "http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/2162923785/#comment72157631190861868", "realname": "Arden", "path_alias": "arden_loc", "author": "35072786@N08", "iconserver": "3331", "datecreate": "1345635876", "_content": "Thanks artolog for the additional information.  We will add more details to the description when we update.", "authorname": "Arden (LOC P&P)", "id": "8602872-2162923785-72157631190861868", "iconfarm": 4}], "photo_id": "2162923785"}}